\c 10
\s Vanakomana vaJafeti, naHamu naShemu
\p
\v 1 Zvino iyi ndiyo rondedzero yemadzinza evanakomana vaNowa, Shemu, Hamu, naJafeti; ivo vakaberekerwa vanakomana shure kwemafashame.
\p
\v 2 Vanakomana vaJafeti: Gomeri, naMagogi naMadhai naJavhani naTubhari naMisheki naTirasi.
\v 3 Nevanakomana vaGomeri: Ashikenazi naRifati naTogarima.
\v 4 Nevanakomana vaJavhani: Erisha naTarishisi naKitimi naDhodhanimu.
\v 5 Nezviwi izvi zvechirudzi zvakagoverwa munyika dzavo umwe neumwe nerurimi rwake, nemhuri dzavo, nendudzi dzavo.
\p
\v 6 Nevanakomana vaHamu: Kushi naMiziraimu naPuti naKenani.
\v 7 Uye vanakomana vaKushi: Sebha naHavhira naSabhita naRama naSabhiteka. Nevanakomana vaRahama: Shebha naDhedhani.
\v 8 Kushi ndokubereka Nimurodhi, iye akatanga kuva une simba panyika.
\v 9 Iye waiva mudzimba une simba pamberi paJehovha; naizvozvo zvinonzi: SaNimurodhi, mudzimba une simba pamberi paJehovha.
\v 10 Uye mavambo eushe hwake aiva paBhabheri neEreki neAkadhi neKarine panyika yeShinari.
\v 11 Kwakabuda kunyika iyo Ashuri, akaenda Asiriya, ndokuvaka Ninivhe neRohobhoti-ire neKara,
\v 12 neReseni pakati peNinivhe neKara (iri iguta guru).
\v 13 Zvino Miziraimu akabereka vaRudhi nevaAnami nevaRehabhi nevaNafituhimu,
\v 14 nevaPaturusi nevaKasiruhi (kwakabva kwaari vaFirisitia) nevaKafutori.
\p
\v 15 Zvino Kenani wakabereka Sidhoni, dangwe rake, naHeti;
\v 16 nevaJebhusi nevaAmori, nevaGirigashi;
\v 17 nevaHivhi, nevaAriki, nevaSini,
\v 18 nevaArivhadhi, nevaZemari, nevaHamati. Shure kwaivava nemhuri dzevaKenani dzakapararira.
\p
\v 19 Zvino muganhu wavaKenani wakabva paSidhoni ukaenda Gerari kusvika Gaza, uchienda Sodhoma neGomora neAdhamu neZibhoimu kusvika paRasha.
\p
\v 20 Ava vanakomana vaHamu, nemhuri dzavo, nendimi dzavo, munyika dzavo, nendudzi dzavo.
\p
\v 21 Naiye Shemu, baba vevana vose vaEbheru, mukuru waJafeti wakaberekerwa vana.
\v 22 Vanakomana vaShemu: Eramu naAshuri, naAripakishadhi naRudhi naAramu.
\v 23 Uye vanakomana vaAramu: Uzi naHuri naGeteri naMashi.
\v 24 Zvino Aripakishadhi wakabereka Shera, Shera ndokubereka Ebheri.
\v 25 Ebheru ndokuberekerwa vanakomana vaviri, zita reumwe \add raiva\add* Peregi, nekuti pamazuva ake nyika yakakamurwa; uye zita remunin'ina wake \add raiva\add* Jokitani.
\v 26 Jokitani ndokubereka Arimodhadhi naSherefi naHazarimavheti naJera
\v 27 naHadhoramu naUsari naDhikira
\v 28 naObhari naAbhimaeri naShebha
\v 29 naOfiri naHavhira naJobhabhu; ava vose \add vaiva\add* vanakomana vaJokitani.
\v 30 Ugaro hwavo hwaitangira paMesha kuenda Sefari, gomo rekumabvazuva.
\v 31 Ava vanakomana vaShemu, nemhuri dzavo nendimi dzavo munyika dzavo, nendudzi dzavo.
\p
\v 32 Ava \add i\add*mhuri dzevanakomana vaNowa, nemazera avo nendudzi dzavo; kwavari kwakaparadzaniswa ndudzi dzose shure kwemvura zhinji.
